<lb n="8"/>reṁṭiki yiṁdula <unclear>golla</unclear> gaṇṭiyabōyuni koḍuku
<lb n="9"/>talliyabōyuni vasamunaṁ beṭṭina Inpaye 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍlu 100 lekkanu Inpayeḍlu nūṟiṁṭiki nitya
<lb n="11" break="no"/><unclear>yapaḍi</unclear> sāniyaṁbāṭi mānika [A]ḍḍeṇḍu ne
